Package mods.railcraft.api.core.items

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IMinecartItem
    This interface should be implemented by any cart item, but it is generally optional.
    IStackFilter
    This interface is used with several of the functions in IItemTransfer to provide a convenient means of dealing with entire classes of items without having to specify each item individually.
    IToolCrowbar  
    ITrackItem
    Should be implemented by any rail item class that wishes to have it's rails placed by for example the Tunnel Bore or Track Relayer.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TagList
    This is a collection of ItemStack tags than can be used with GameRegistry.findItemStack().
